            <description><![CDATA[【玩命打工，眼快瞎了！一个动作缓解眼疲劳<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[晕]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_yun-3ca5d0a5b7.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】比打工人更累的，是打工人的眼睛，不仅要陪着你996、007，下班后还得“加班”刷手机<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[二哈]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_erha-139d0e07bd.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>小卫给你支招，帮你缓解眼疲劳：按一按四白穴，每次按揉2～3分钟，顺时针、逆时针各按揉20次，戳视频，学起来👇<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（CCTV生活圈） <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4939396919787574" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">CCTV生活圈的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/orj480/713e54f1ly1hhbf0k3rmdj21hc0u0n1a.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/S4e7zyBUlx0888rE0bRK01041200uImr0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1693545260&amp;ssig=otyZM%2BiYYs&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/4cQNnrz4lx0888rDiEUU01041200f6fJ0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1693545260&amp;ssig=POmM%2BtqHrk&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/BB0aYwaBlx0888rCMws80104120099MT0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1693545260&amp;ssig=xBAVevOQVe&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4939396